Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister-in-law, please board the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:30.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Crossing the Yellow River is crossing into Héběi's borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I will be able to see my elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Who couldn't but only reflect in longing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:56.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Bidding farewell to Xǔchāng, \Nhanging my seal and locking that gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:00.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Cutting down the warriors of the pass, in order to look for my elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:07.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,To see my elder brother's face, I, Guān Yúnchǎng, would die for it a myriad times without regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,370.53)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1720,2080)}Sūn Qián\NStyled: Gōngyòu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu! Where were you after we were defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wandered around Rǔnán!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I fled from Xú Province, I wandered Rǔnán.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I luckily met {\i1}Liú Pì{\i0}, who gave me shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent to Héběi to ally with Yuán Shào,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and invite Xuándé together to defeat Cáo (Cāo).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yuán Shào's strategists resent each other and fight for influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shào himself is suspicious and indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Uncle and I decided to find a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he has already left to Rǔnán.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid you would be harmed by Yuán Shào upon arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I was sent to meet you.\NTis fortunate I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, you can hurry to\NRǔnán to meet with our lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The road has been long and arduous, to think it has come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistresses, is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-law, don't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The imperial uncle is at Rǔnán.\NIn a few days, you can meet him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you, sir, had not escorted us through the passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us would never see the imperial uncle ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Guān Yǔ, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop Guan Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Sūn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard the chariot. I will deal with this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, I will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(132.05,168.621)}Xiàhóu Dūn\NStyled: Yuánràng
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}If you come for me, it would be breaking the Chancellor's promsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}The Chancellor did not send out a written word,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}yet you trespass \Nand kill our warriors along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}This cannot be tolerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}Today, I'm here to capture you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}Bring you back to the Chancellor in chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}The Chancellor made it clear that going forward, no matter what happens or who dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}I answer to no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}Yet those gate-guards were arbitrary \Nand wanted me stopped despite my reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}I had to resort to violence in order to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)\i1}Had it been any other officer, there'd be no quarrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)\i1}But Qín Qí was my subordinate, and my friend Cài Yáng's nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)\i1}How can I back down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you cannot fight with Yúnchǎng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chancellor admires General Guān's virtue, so he was stopped by the gate-passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so he commanded me to relay the order to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guān Yǔ killed those gate-officers to trespass!\NDoes the Chancellor know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I will arrest Guān Yǔ and take him back to the Chancellor for questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not challenge me, knave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we will decide who is the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,General, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,General, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,General, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I received the Chancellor's order to arrest Guān Yǔ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Chancellor was worried and had me to pass this letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He ordered that the passes were not to hinder General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Chancellor know of the killings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if he does not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, now you have disobeyed the Chancellor's orders multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I killed Qín Qí?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you are here to resolve this grievance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I will not hesitate killing\N the Chancellor's trusted officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be thus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(601,350.227)\fade(255,0,255,0,460,1420,1780)}Zhāng Liáo \NStyled: Wényuǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By the Chancellor's orders! He heard of Yúnchǎng's battles, and feared the passes would still halt him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so he sent me throughout the gate-passes to grant him passage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Qín Qí is Cài Yáng's nephew, he entrusted him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Guān Yǔ killed him, how could I ever rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cài will have to resolve it himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but by the Chancellor's generosity, Yúnchǎng has passage. We cannot disobey that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, we shall meet again on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, where are you going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where my elder brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know where Xuándé is,\Nwould you like to join the Chancellor again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How would that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wényuǎn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the way, I committed a many misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go back, please tell the Chancellor I ask for his forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave your horses and weapons behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you wretches to have the gall to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How amusing! Now leave your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just a bunch of petty horse-thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Men, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismount! Leave your weapons behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Péi) Yuánshào, stop! \NWe are making a huge mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhōu Cāng pays his respects to General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This man had reported that there was someone riding a fast steed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed over at his family's house and he invited us to steal such a steed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We never knew it was yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero, Guān Yúnchǎng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are fortunate to meet with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have never met before, how did you know of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then general, the Imperial Uncle, \Nand Zhāng Yìdé beat that county inspector at Ānxǐ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The court distributed wanted posters everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, we have never forgotten your integrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:13:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always been eager to see you, and here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, you may all stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have travelled a thousand lǐ, escorting my\Nsisters-in-laws to find my elder brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,all on this horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are, having the gall to plot against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For his family's sake, spare his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Return to where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do not fool around with petty crime henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long admired your virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(619,337.03)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2260)}Zhōu Cāng
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I am blessed to see you, my life has purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing to follow you everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lead your carriage and your horse willingly, and I am content with death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, please mount your horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,'Mount your horse'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, please mount your horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, please mount your horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, may I ask what is the land behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten lǐ before me is Gǔchéng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasten our march! We will rest once we arrive at Gǔchéng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you officials, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A few days ago, there was a mighty man descending from the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He entered the city, asking for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The county magistrate refused. \NThat man got so furious he seized the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He seized the city and exiled the magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That man now recruits soldiers and horses and has been storing provisions in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He now has three to five thousand soldiers, no one dares to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, do you know this man's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Zhāng Fēi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Fēi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We found Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He is ahead in Gǔchéng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.36,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(603.568,358)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What weapon you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything will do, but preferably something like {\i1}the Green Dragon-Crescent Blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,just like what General Guān uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being forgetful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday they did remind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,only sir can refer to General Guān.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No one else can talk about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I- Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yide?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Yìdé! Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sūn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sūn, any news of my Elder Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of our Imperial Uncle, we can discuss later in detail
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Yúnchǎng is escorting your\Ntwo sisters-in-law to Gǔchéng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé, are you not happy to welcome him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yìdé that's picking us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My third brother is coming to welcome us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-law! Yìdé is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor, face my spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Guān Yǔ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are Guān Yǔ, but\Ntoday, it is Guān Yǔ that will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten our Oath of the Peach Garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have have no shame! How dare you meet with me face to face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How have I no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You betrayed my elder brother, you surrendered to Cáo Cāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and even accepted a marquis title, \Nand now you've come to deceive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, it's complicated. It's hard to explain right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask our sisters-in-law here yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you do this, brother-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait there sisters-in-law. I will kill this traitor first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall escort you back in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother-in-law! He didn't know where you and Imperial Uncle were,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he had to reside at Cáo's camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that imperial uncle is in Runan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he escorted us all the way over all obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame him, Third brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A loyal man would rather die than surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man would serve two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you accuse me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng came back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you lie to me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he come for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He clearly came to capture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to capture you, I would bring an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that, if not an army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still dare to argue?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Second Brother!\N-Third brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.63,0:24:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My good brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you, my Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.88,0:24:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.58,0:25:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān is still as strong as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.52,0:25:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No need, no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.82,0:25:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.66,0:25:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyday, General Zhāng misses the imperial uncle and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.08,0:25:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He often wakes up screaming your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.67,0:25:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You met today and yet he almost killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.68,0:25:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That is no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.56,0:25:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Usually General Zhāng doesn't allow us to speak of General Guān.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.55,0:25:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do, general would get violently angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.35,0:25:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé is very clear-cut, he detests evil and unjust.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.62,0:25:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.66,0:25:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,308.515)}Lady Mí
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.56,0:25:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had gone on each other's throats today, would Second Brother-in-Law still say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.13,0:26:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters-in-Law! Second-Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.30,0:26:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.00,0:26:08.87,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,365.455)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1720,2080)} Mí Zhú \NStyled: Zi Zhòng
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.41,0:26:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.74,0:26:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.88,0:26:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we've reunited, the one only missing is Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.62,0:26:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I will go to look for him in Runan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.69,0:26:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When we came here, we heard my lord, seeing Liu Pì and Gōng Dū were low on manpower,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.92,0:26:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,has gone to negotiate with Yuán Shào.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Zhou Cang\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.45,0:26:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How many serve under Pei Yuanshao?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.48,0:26:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,About four or five hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.52,0:26:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take a shortcut to look for Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.26,0:26:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You go gather some men in Mount Wòniú, and return through the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.52,0:27:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.13,0:27:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This old city is our safe haven. We can't abandon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.71,0:27:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will look for Elder Brother with Mr. Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.74,0:27:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you stay here and guard the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.71,0:27:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.15,0:27:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry, brother. \NCome back as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.29,0:28:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there is Hebei.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.43,0:28:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tread lightly, general.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.87,0:28:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only take rest for a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.63,0:28:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wait for me to meet with Imperial Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.57,0:28:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gongyou, please be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.51,0:28:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.57,0:28:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.45,0:29:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, if you are so eager to see Yúnchǎng,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.42,0:29:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,why won't you see Yuán Shào tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.02,0:29:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him you will go to Jīng-Province to\Npersuade Liú Biǎo in allying against Cáo Cāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.32,0:29:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shào agreed. My lord, you can seize this opportunity to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.64,0:29:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Its a good plan, but I wonder if\Nyou, Lord Jiǎn, can accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.56,0:29:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, no need to be worried! \NI, Jiǎn Yōng, will find a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Another prolonged and painful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.46,0:30:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Jǐngshēng has the nine commanderies of the Jīng-Province. We can join together against Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.28,0:30:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I already sent someone for such purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.89,0:30:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That useless Liú Biǎo refused alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.32,0:30:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We share the same family ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.64,0:30:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were sent, I would have\Nno trouble convincing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.82,0:30:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If Liú Biǎo and I unite together...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.00,0:30:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But he did defeat Liú Pì several times...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.08,0:30:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, you can go negotiate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.28,0:30:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I shall go immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.15,0:30:48.52,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600.089,341.333)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1720,2080)}Yuán Shào\N Styled: Běnchū
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.30,0:30:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard recently that Yúnchǎng has left Cáo Cāo and intends to come to Héběi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.44,0:31:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill him, to avenge Yán Liáng and Wén Chǒu!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.27,0:31:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}Sire once said you wanted Yúncháng by your side, so I sent him a letter. Why do you want to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.89,0:31:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}Besides, Yán Liáng and Wén Chǒu are but two deers, while Yúncháng is a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.68,0:31:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.431,452.212)}Two deers for a tiger, what is there to hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.73,0:31:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking in jest. In reality, I do like Yúncháng.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.77,0:31:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Xuande can call someone to get him here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.47,0:31:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, I, Liu Bei shall have \NSun Qian to call Yúncháng back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.64,0:31:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Farewell.\N-Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.80,0:31:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that man leaves, he'll never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.58,0:31:57.58,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1720,2080)\pos(101.407,338)}Guō Tú\NStyled: Gōngzé
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.00,0:32:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.54,0:32:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.02,0:32:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, my father asked me to bring water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.85,0:32:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,General, you stood here for too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.67,0:32:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please put on this robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.71,0:32:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,General, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.83,0:32:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him! It's him! It's my elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.52,0:32:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.47,0:32:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.00,0:32:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Elder Brother\N-Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Brother\N-My Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.44,0:32:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.68,0:32:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.15,0:33:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, we've been apart far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.70,0:33:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Píng'er, come! Come meet with your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.17,0:33:13.48,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(101.407,327)}Guān Píng
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.87,0:33:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.51,0:33:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, this is my son {\i1}Guān Píng{\i0}. \NI adopted him in Guanding village.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.45,0:33:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This one greet you, my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.26,0:33:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.96,0:33:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.92,0:34:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guan!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.43,0:34:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guan! Zhou Cang greets you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.27,0:34:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You were contact Pei Yuanshao. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.54,0:34:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,General, before I reached Mount Woniu,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.88,0:34:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a warrior on horseback, he engaged Pei Yuanshao.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.86,0:34:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed Pei Yuanshao in an instant, and took over the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.05,0:34:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to call,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.89,0:34:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,only these few dared to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.16,0:34:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest were too afraid to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I challenged that warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.70,0:34:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but lost to him, injured by his spear three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.17,0:34:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this man? What does he look like
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.21,0:35:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He is mighty, but I don't know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's someone this powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.81,0:35:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way, I will meet with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.48,0:35:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.06,0:35:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, you brigand! Today will be your last!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.55,0:35:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,General, that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.37,0:35:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sir {\i1}Zǐlóng?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.72,0:35:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir magister!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.69,0:35:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir magister!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.68,0:36:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Zilong!\N-Magister!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.52,0:36:16.48,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1720,2080)\pos(122.859,338)}Zhào Yún\NStyled: Zǐlóng
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.48,0:36:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.42,0:36:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I bid magister farewell,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.22,0:36:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gongsun Zan became callous, \Nand led everyone go down with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.16,0:36:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shào called on me many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I refused to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.86,0:36:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when I heard you were at Yuán Shào's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.96,0:36:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,had I want to come, but I didn't want to meet with Yuán Shào.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.64,0:36:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was scattered with the wind. \NYet when I was passing by,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.04,0:36:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that Pei Yuanshao came down to rob my horse, I killed him in self-defense, and took refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.01,0:36:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am overjoyed to see the magister again!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.42,0:36:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To meet again today, it's truly a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.86,0:36:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had wandered across \Nall directions, looking for a worthy lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.46,0:37:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But none were as worthy as you, magister. To meet again, is truly a great honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.78,0:37:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Through thick and thin,\N I shall follow you to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.25,0:37:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yide has come to welcome us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.20,0:37:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Days have been like years! Today, we will reunite!
